Shadow Caller			KEY:Spiritualist Archetype ~ Shadow Caller						CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.SpiritualistArchetype																							PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Shadow Caller],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Spiritualist_Archetype_Spellcasting=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_Phantom=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_SharedConsciousness=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_EthericTether=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_PhantomRecall=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_EmpoweredConsciousness=True]																																																									DESC:While most spiritualists form a bond with the remnants of a creature's soul, some explore ways to bind ephemeral shadows to their own souls in exchange for power.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Shadowcaster|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Shade|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Emotionless|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Weakening Touch|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Umbral Shroud|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=7	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Caster|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=12	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Midnight Shroud|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=17	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Inhabit Shadow|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Bound|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Jump|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ See in Darkness|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Umbral Aura|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=10	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Caller ~ Living Darkness|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=20																																																																																																																																														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.50																																																																																											FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_Spellcasting|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_Phantom|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_SharedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_EthericTether|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_PhantomRecall|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_EmpoweredConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_Phantom|false	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_SharedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_EthericTether|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_PhantomRecall|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_FusedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_EmpoweredConsciousness|true
Zeitgeist Binder			KEY:Spiritualist Archetype ~ Zeitgeist Binder						CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.SpiritualistArchetype																							PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Zeitgeist Binder],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Spiritualist_Archetype_Phantom=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_DetectUndead=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_CalmSpirit=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_CallSpirit=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_BondedSenses=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness=True]																																																																				DESC:Not all spiritualists deal in the souls of creatures that refuse to pass into death. Zeitgeist binders channel the emotional connections of a group of people into a unique phantom that personifies a community.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Zeitgeist Binder ~ Zeitgeist|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Zeitgeist Binder ~ Settlement Aspect|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Zeitgeist Binder ~ Settlement Avatar|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=2																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.51																																																																																											FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_Phantom|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_DetectUndead|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_CalmSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_CallSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_BondedSenses|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_DetectUndead|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_CalmSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_CallSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_BondedSenses|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_FusedConsciousness|true

#Shadow Caller
Shadowcaster			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Shadowcaster								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																											DESC:A shadow caller adds darkness and deeper darkness to their class spell list as 2nd- and 3rd-level spells, respectively. When her shade (see below) inhabits her shadow, the shadow caller's effective caster level is one higher when she casts all spells with the shadow or darkness descriptor. This ability alters the spiritualist's spellcasting.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.50																																																																															SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Spiritualist=2|Darkness|Spiritualist=3|Deeper Darkness
Shade					KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Shade									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																											DESC:A shadow caller gains a special kind of phantom known as a shade. A shade functions as a phantom, except as noted below. A shade is from the Shadow Plane instead of the Ethereal Plane. A shade is not confined to the shadow caller's consciousness, but instead inhabits her shadow. This ability alters phantom.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Inhabit Shadow			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Inhabit Shadow								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A shade resides within a shadow caller's own shadow. When the shade is summoned, the shadow caller does not cast a shadow under any circumstances. Creatures that don't normally cast shadows (such as vampires) cannot be shadow callers. While the shade inhabits its master's shadow, the shadow caller gains a +4 circumstance bonus on Stealth checks against creatures without darkvision or the see in darkness ability; at 12th level, this bonus increases to +8. Additionally, the shadow caller gains darkvision 60 feet while her shade inhabits her shadow. If the shadow caller already has darkvision, its range increases by 30 feet.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Shadow Bound			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Bound								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A shadow caller's shade remains stable while adjacent to the shadow caller, or while up to 5 feet away from the shadow caller for every 5 levels the shadow caller possesses. If the shade moves beyond this distance, it is automatically dismissed back to the Shadow Plane (preventing the shade from being summoned back for 24 hours) unless the shadow caller concentrates as per the etheric tether ability. However, if both the shadow caller and shade are in areas of total darkness, the shade can move any distance from the shadow caller. If the shade is beyond its maximum distance and enters an area of dim or brighter illumination, it immediately returns to the Shadow Plane and cannot be summoned for 24 hours.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Shadow Jump				KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Jump								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:At 6th level, when a shadow caller's shade inhabits her shadow, she can travel between shadows as per the shadowdancer's shadow jump ability. Each day, she can travel a total of 40 feet per spiritualist level in this way and, as with a shadowdancer, the distance is rounded to the nearest 10-foot increment.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.50
See in Darkness			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ See in Darkness								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:At 9th level, a shadow caller can gain the see in darkness universal monster ability as a standard action. She can use this ability for a number of rounds per day equal to her spiritualist level, though these rounds need not be consecutive.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Umbral Aura				KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Umbral Aura								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																							DESC:At 10th level, a shadow caller is wreathed in an aura of darkness while her shade inhabits her shadow, gaining 50%% concealment against creatures without darkvision or the see in darkness ability. Additionally, the shadow caller's square and all adjacent squares are treated as areas of dim illumination while she benefits from this ability; this second effect counts as a 4th-level darkness spell for the purpose of adjudicating light and darkness effects. While her shade inhabits her shadow, the shadow caller can hide in plain sight, even if an observing creature has darkvision or see in darkness.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Living Darkness			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Living Darkness								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:At 20th level, a shadow caller becomes a creature of absolute darkness. When using her incorporeal bonded manifestation, she is immune to cold and mind-affecting effects and gains an incorporeal touch attack that she can use as a standard action to deal 20d6 points of negative energy damage. When the shadow caller damages a creature with this ability, she gains 5d6 temporary hit points (Fortitude half; DC %1), so long as she doesn't already have any temporary hit points gained via this ability. Temporary hit points gained this way disappear after 1 hour.|20+WIS																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.50

Emotionless				KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Emotionless			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 1	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A shadow caller's shade lacks an emotional focus; it is cold and devoid of all emotions. The shade gains a number of ranks in Intimidate and Stealth equal to its Hit Dice. The shadow caller gains Skill Focus in each of these skills while the shade inhabits her shadow. The shade has good Reflex and Will saves, gains Lightning Reflexes as a bonus feat, and gains the following abilities.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Weakening Touch			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Weakening Touch			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2a	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A shade's slam attack causes its victim to take a -2 penalty to Strength for 1 round. As a standard action, a shade in incorporeal form can deliver the penalty as a touch attack. This penalty does not stack with itself. This is a negative energy effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Umbral Shroud			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Umbral Shroud			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2b	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:When the shadow caller reaches 7th level, her shade can emit a 10-foot aura of swirling shadows that grants all allies 20%% concealment against creatures without darkvision or the see in darkness ability, and a +4 bonus on Stealth checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Shadow Caster			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Shadow Caster			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2c	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																										DESC:When the shadow caller reaches 12th level, her shade gains the ability to cast either shadow conjuration or shadow evocation once per day. It uses its Hit Dice as its caster level, and the DC for these spells equals 10 + 1/2 the shade's Hit Dice + its Charisma modifier. Instead of the normal spell level and percentage of reality for the two spells, the maximum spell level of the duplicated spell is 4th level, and the effects are 40%% real. When the shadow caller reaches 18th level, the maximum spell level improves to 6th level and effects are 60%% real.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Midnight Shroud			KEY:Shadow Caller ~ Midnight Shroud			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2d	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ShadowCallerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:When the shadow caller reaches 17th level, her shade's umbral shroud also lowers the light level in its range to darkness, regardless of the prevailing conditions; this counts as a 7th-level darkness spell for the purpose of adjudicating light and darkness effects.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.50

#Zeitgeist Binder
Zeitgeist				KEY:Zeitgeist Binder ~ Zeitgeist								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ZeitgeistBinderClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A zeitgeist binder's phantom is called a zeitgeist. In addition to an emotion, a zeitgeist is tied to one aspect of its settlement: corruption, crime, economy, law, lore, or society (GameMastery Guide p204). In order to select an aspect, that aspect of the settlement must have a positive modifier (for instance, a settlement with a negative lore modifier or a modifier of 0 could not manifest a lore zeitgeist). Although a zeitgeist personifies a single chosen settlement, a zeitgeist binder can call it anywhere, but outside the bounds of its settlement, it loses the benefits of its settlement aspect and settlement avatar abilities. This ability alters phantom.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.51
Settlement Aspect			KEY:Zeitgeist Binder ~ Settlement Aspect							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ZeitgeistBinderClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																									DESC:A zeitgeist binder gains a number of spell-like abilities tied to her zeitgeist's settlement aspect. Other than being based on Wisdom instead of Charisma, these work the same way as the fractured mind's emotional power ability (Occult Adventures p109).	DESC:&nl;Corruption: Conditional favor UI (5th), false belief UI (7th), charm person (9th), mass suggestion UI (16th).	DESC:&nl;Crime: Crime of opportunity UI (5th), pilfering hand UC (7th), demand offering OA (9th), crime wave UI (16th).	DESC:&nl;Economy: Crafter's fortune APG (5th), masterwork transformation APG (7th), beguiling gift (9th), major creation (16th). The masterwork transformation spell-like ability does not ignore the material component.	DESC:&nl;Law: Detect chaos (5th), arrow of law UM (7th), peacebond UC (9th), mark of justice (16th).	DESC:&nl;Lore: Object reading OA (5th), hypercognition OA (7th), heightened awareness ACG (9th), legend lore (16th).	DESC:&nl;Society: Cultural adaptation UI (5th), rumormonger UI (7th), share language APG (9th), coordinated effort APG (16th).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.51
Settlement Avatar			KEY:Zeitgeist Binder ~ Settlement Avatar							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Features.ZeitgeistBinderClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																									DESC:When a zeitgeist binder reaches 2nd level, the zeitgeist becomes a living avatar of the settlement. As a standard action, it can project its senses out into the settlement, perceiving the general pulse of its chosen aspect throughout the whole settlement as well as anything involving its aspect that is occurring within 50 feet per spiritualist level. The sensing works like enter image, so the zeitgeist attempts a Perception check at a -10 penalty to notice any particular activity within range. The zeitgeist can use this ability for a number of rounds per day equal to the zeitgeist binder's spiritualist level. These rounds need not be consecutive. When the zeitgeist binder reaches 10th level, the zeitgeist can project its senses to feel its settlement aspect at will. Additionally, the zeitgeist binder gains a bonus teamwork feat as long as she is in her zeitgeist's settlement. The zeitgeist binder must meet the teamwork feat's prerequisites, and she grants the feat as a bonus feat to her zeitgeist, even if it doesn't meet the prerequisites.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.51

